Christiane F. (born Vera Christiane Felscherinow on May 20, 1962) is a former heroin addict famous for her contribution to the autobiographical book Wir Kinder vom Bahnhof Zoo, and this film &quot;Christiane F&quot; based on the book, which describes her struggle with various forms of drug addiction during her teens.

A realistic and cautionary tale of teenage heroin addiction. If you are a parent or teacher and want to show your children the reality of heroin, this is the film to show.

